# Unit Tests

- Test ViewModels, Use Cases, Repositories; mock network with `URLProtocol`.
- Deterministic tests only; no real network.

# UI Tests

- Cover onboarding, OTP login, recording, playback, and logout flows.
- Use accessibility identifiers for selectors.

# Coverage & Regression

- Maintain meaningful coverage on core logic.
- Add tests for any fixed bug.
